Loops:
 It is used to repeat instructions.

■ 1) While Loop:

⫸ Syntax:

Create Iterator
While Condition:
  Statement 
  Iteration ↑ / ↓


# Code - While Loop
i)
Count = 1                     # Count is Iterator
while Count <= 5:             # Stopping Condition
  print(Count)
  Count += 1                  # Loop 1 = Iteration 1

- O/P.:
1
2
3
4
5



⫸ Break & Continue:

⫸ Break:
    It is used to terminate the loop when encountered.

# Code - Break
i)
Count = 1                     
while Count <= 5:            
  print(Count)
  
  if (Count == 3):
    break

  Count += 1

- O/P.:
1
2
3
